---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import kaiMcKimImage from '../assets/kaimckim.png';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Kai McKim - Tutor at New Leaf Academy" description="Meet Kai McKim, a specialist English tutor at New Leaf Academy." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="bio-container">
				<div class="bio-header">
					<Image
						src={kaiMcKimImage}
						alt="Kai McKim, Tutor at New Leaf Academy"
						class="bio-headshot"
						width={200}
						height={200}
					/>
					<div class="header-text">
						<h1>Kai McKim</h1>
						<p class="role">Specialist English Tutor</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="bio-content">
					<h2>About Kai</h2>
					<p>
						After gaining excellent grades in GCSE and A-Level, including A*s in English Literature and Language, Kai went to The Bartlett at UCL to study architecture, widely considered the best architecture school in the world.
					</p>
					<p>
						Towards the end of his degree, he was asked to give lectures to first-year students where he discovered the joy of teaching and passing knowledge on to others. His love of English has only grown since he started tutoring online in 2024. With his head always in a book and constantly writing journals and books, his passion for the subject is infectious.
					</p>
					<p>
						His students have achieved results better than anyone expected, and he is eager to help more. Whilst tutoring, he has used his architecture degree to build a studio in his garden from scratchâ€”an incredible feat of patience, hard work, and creative design.
					</p>
					<p>
						He believes all students have the potential to succeed in English and wishes to help his students achieve this.
					</p>
				</div>
                <div class="cta-section">
                    <h2>Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2>
                    <p>Dan is ready to help you or your child achieve academic success. Book a friendly, no-obligation chat today.</p>
                    <a href="/consultations" class="cta-button">
                        Book Your Free Consultation
                    </a>
                </div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		--card-bg-color: #f9f9f9;
        --box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	main {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 2em auto;
		padding: 0 1em;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.bio-container {
		background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
		padding: 2em;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	}

	.bio-header {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2em;
		gap: 1em;
	}

	.bio-headshot {
		width: clamp(150px, 30vw, 200px);
		height: clamp(150px, 30vw, 200px);
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 50%;
		border: 5px solid var(--accent);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
	}

	.header-text h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2em, 6vw, 2.8em);
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.header-text .role {
		font-size: clamp(1.1em, 3vw, 1.3em);
		font-weight: bold;
		color: var(--accent-pop);
		margin-top: 0.25em;
	}

	.bio-content h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5em, 5vw, 2em);
		color: var(--accent);
		border-bottom: 2px solid #e9eafc;
		padding-bottom: 0.5em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}

	.bio-content p {
		font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}

        .cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 2em;
		padding: 2em;
		background-color: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	
	.cta-section h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
		margin-top: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

    .cta-section p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    }

	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1em 2em;
		background-color: var(--accent-pop);
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		.bio-header {
			flex-direction: row;
			text-align: left;
			gap: 2em;
		}
	}
</style>
